16
00:01:50,079 --> 00:01:51,096
Don't you dare mess it up!

17
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,400
How stupid can you be?

18
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,359
All of this... is for love.

19
00:02:33,479 --> 00:02:34,039
Hey.

20
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:35,159
My baby Yoki

21
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,400
I already chewed out that

22
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:37,599
selfish director.

23
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:39,240
Calm down first, okay?

24
00:02:39,879 --> 00:02:40,400
I just hope

25
00:02:40,639 --> 00:02:41,639
that you won't leave.

26
00:02:41,919 --> 00:02:43,280
We're in a tough spot right now,

27
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:43,960
