28
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,640
If you wanna turn things around,

29
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:47,216
you gotta endure a little hardship.

30
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,039
That's why I didn't ask you to

31
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:49,199
bring an assistant.

32
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,000
I really hope you'll stay.

33
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:53,520
Good boy.

34
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,000
Then get a good night's sleep, ok?

35
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:56,520
Wait.

36
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:58,216
You're still answering calls this late?

37
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,280
Another sleepless night?

38
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:00,599
Not exactly.

39
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:04,159
I think I've found

40
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,719
my magic cure.

41
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:19,000
This feeling of deep sleep is truly

42
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:21,680
long overdue.

43
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:25,479
So nice!

44
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:30,960
Pervert!

45
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,479
I love my wife very much.

46
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,080
My wife made me who I am.

47
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,639
My wife became my wife.

48
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:43,439
My house became my home.

49
00:03:43,719 --> 00:03:45,199
She's a very virtuous woman.

50
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,400
Get to the point.

51
00:03:46,599 --> 00:03:47,719
Mr. Yoki.

52
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:49,719
I was wrong about what happened today.

53
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:50,280
This variety show,

54
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,615
I've been working for it for eight years.

55
