I don't want to lose my wife.

56
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,000
You're going to quit?

57
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,560
But you're a volunteer.

58
00:03:58,919 --> 00:04:00,400
Do you know what a volunteer is?

59
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,879
We haven't even started
rolling and you're backing out.

60
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:04,559
What are we going to do about this?

61
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:05,639
But.

62
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,680
If you really don't want to participate,

63
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:08,719
I will never

64
