67
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,000
I know what to do.

68
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:15,159
Village Chief.

69
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,519
Magic cure Yang Meng.

70
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,079
Miracle for insomnia.

71
