Here he comes.

72
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:02,759
Mr. Yoki.

73
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,639
Where are your shoes?

74
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,560
I can't find them.

75
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:12,120
It's okay, this is fine.

76
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,560
