79
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,720
You'll definitely win!

80
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,920
Mr. Yoki.

81
00:05:31,839 --> 00:05:33,399
It hasn't started yet.

82
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:41,600
The first segment.

83
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:44,720
Our guests have to compete for.

84
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:47,360
Lanwan Village's specialty ingredients,

85
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,120
and then

86
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,399
