90
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,600
Ready?

91
00:05:57,639 --> 00:05:58,439
Brother Yoki.

92
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,600
Good luck!

93
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,360
You too!

94
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,720
Take your positions!

95
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,560
Alright!

96
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,920
Please continue the competition, everyone!

97
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,360
