102
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,600
Be careful!

103
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:54,920
Slow down.

104
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:55,920
Take it easy.

105
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,360
It hurts so much.

106
00:06:58,839 --> 00:06:59,879
Then be careful!

107
00:07:03,519 --> 00:07:04,079
Slow down, slow down...

108
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,240
Walk slower.

109
00:07:05,399 --> 00:07:06,839
Okay, slow down...

110
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,600
I... I...

111
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,336
What's wrong with your program team?

112
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:15,336
Leaving the guests injured like this
and doing nothing about it—it's dangerous!

113
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:17,295
He's totally different from
how he was in high school.

114
00:07:17,319 --> 00:07:18,759
He's changed so much.

115
00:07:22,439 --> 00:07:23,439
Don't move!

116
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:27,759
Don't move!

117
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:40,479
Didn't expect you're quite professional.

118
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:42,480
I'm a volunteer in the village now.

119
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,040
The work is quite diverse.

120
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,800
