121
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:51,240
Nice jawline.

122
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,000
Great skin too.

123
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:55,759
How come I didn't
notice that in high school?

124
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,120
He's quite handsome.

125
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,480
It might hurt a bit.

126
00:08:23,759 --> 00:08:24,759
It's okay.

127
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,680
Do whatever you want with me.

128
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,040
Anything is fine.

129
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,080
Ouch...

130
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,960
