139
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,399
Fine, I'll get up myself.

140
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,120
Alright, alright, I'll help you.

141
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,720
I...

142
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:21,120
Are you trying to save me

143
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,320
