145
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,320
Mr. Yoki.

146
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:31,919
It's a successful first battle.

147
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,320
Idiot.

148
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:43,559
Damn pervert!

149
