158
00:10:01,399 --> 00:10:01,960
What are you doing?

159
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,840
Just checking, I'm worried it's serious.

160
00:10:04,039 --> 00:10:05,200
Told you it's fine!

161
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:31,679
Did he just glare at me?

162
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,720
I don't know.

163
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,440
No need

164
00:10:36,759 --> 00:10:37,759
I'm afraid it hurts.

165
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,960
It doesn't hurt at all.

166
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:46,840
The tide's gone out.

167
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,799
Let's go tide pooling!

168
00:10:56,399 --> 00:10:57,399
Mr. Yoki.

169
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,159
We're about to move on to

170
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,320
