171
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:04,159
You made ten tiny bites
out of that one green onion.

172
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,080
Are you reluctant to eat it

173
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:08,679
or waiting for someone to feed you?

174
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:10,039
No, not at all.

175
00:11:11,039 --> 00:11:12,080
It looks delicious.

176
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,240
Alright.

177
00:11:18,399 --> 00:11:19,399
Great.

178
00:11:20,679 --> 00:11:21,679
Tonight

179
00:11:22,559 --> 00:11:23,559
