196
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:30,200
Damn pervert!

197
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:32,679
Yoki.

198
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,480
I don't feel right about this.

199
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,240
Why don't you come stay with me?

200
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:37,679
There's definitely enough space.

201
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:42,319
