206
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,240
You want to eat it?

207
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:57,559
Come here.

208
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,519
So violent!

209
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,120
But so charming!

210
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,440
What are you doing?

211
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,200
What are you eating?

212
00:13:21,399 --> 00:13:22,399
Is it good?

213
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:23,799
Give me a bite.

214
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:35,360
It's delicious!

215
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,120
You...

216
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,240
