217
00:13:42,759 --> 00:13:43,759
No, I'm not.

218
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:01,120
You're scared of me.

219
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:07,639
N-No, I'm not.

220
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:10,440
No?

221
00:14:11,919 --> 00:14:12,919
Really?

222
00:14:14,039 --> 00:14:15,039
Really.

223
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,320
Alright.

224
00:14:21,559 --> 00:14:22,759
The place I'm staying tonight,

225
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,120
I can't read the map.

226
00:14:24,799 --> 00:14:25,799
Show me the way.

227
00:14:27,559 --> 00:14:28,080
I'm only responsible for

228
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,519
safety issues.

229
00:14:36,679 --> 00:14:37,679
Ok fine.

230
00:14:40,679 --> 00:14:42,079
What kind of old classmate are you?

231
00:14:42,639 --> 00:14:44,239
Haven't seen each other for eight years,

232
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,800
no wonder there's no friendship left.

233
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:47,440
Leaving me here

234
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:48,879
on this lonely island

235
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,879
to fend for myself.

236
00:15:02,639 --> 00:15:03,120
Coincidentally

237
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,640
I'm on my way to do something.

238
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,200
If you can get on,

239
00:15:06,519 --> 00:15:07,519
I'll give you a ride.

240
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,360
Are you out of your mind?

241
00:15:13,559 --> 00:15:14,559
Yang Meng,

242
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,639
Why did you bring me to your house?

243
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,920
This is where you're staying tonight.

244
00:16:01,799 --> 00:16:02,879
This is where I'm staying!

245
00:16:03,519 --> 00:16:04,519
Come on in.

246
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,120
We're here.

247
00:16:19,159 --> 00:16:20,159
This is it.

248
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,919
Live here alone?

249
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:29,639
I might die here

250
00:16:29,679 --> 00:16:30,679
