251
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:32,360
Impossible.

252
00:16:32,399 --> 00:16:33,399
Look,

253
00:16:34,279 --> 00:16:35,799
this open-air space is cool.

254
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,360
This curtain,

255
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:38,600
this table,

256
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:40,840
