258
00:16:47,639 --> 00:16:48,639
Sturdy?

259
00:16:49,279 --> 00:16:50,720
Maybe...

260
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,200
I can make you a hammock.

261
00:16:54,159 --> 00:16:55,279
Or.

262
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:58,320
Or... or...

263
00:16:58,639 --> 00:16:59,919
Why don't you stay here

264
00:17:00,039 --> 00:17:01,039
and sleep with me?

265
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:03,000
I'm really scared living alone.

266
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:06,119
Didn't you plan this

267
00:17:06,279 --> 00:17:07,480
