268
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,400
No.

269
00:17:10,559 --> 00:17:11,599
How could I?

270
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:13,640
Fine.

271
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:14,319
Then I'm not helping.

272
00:17:14,559 --> 00:17:15,559
