280
00:17:39,039 --> 00:17:40,039
Is it here?

281
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:41,440
A little further in.

282
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:44,720
Here?

283
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:45,960
Further in.

284
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:47,480
This one.

285
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:00,960
Come back.

286
00:18:02,519 --> 00:18:03,960
Let go.

287
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,680
It's a bit salty.

288
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:10,240
H-His tongue.

289
00:18:11,440 --> 00:18:12,440
What are you doing?

290
00:18:13,039 --> 00:18:14,039
I have a toothache.

291
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:16,200
Then go to the clinic.

292
00:18:16,519 --> 00:18:17,039
Let's go.

293
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:18,240
Wait a minute.

294
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:19,680
Turn around.

295
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:21,240
Turn around.

